  "detailed_description": "One night the moon, which normally shone bright and white, had turned a deep, eerie shade of red. As the night wore on, people began to feel strange. They felt a hunger deep inside them, a hunger that could not be satisfied. It wasn't long before they began to turn on each other, attacking and biting those around them.<br>Before anyone knew it, people started to turn into zombies. They roamed the streets, seeking out any remaining survivors to feed on. Towns were overrun with the undead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Explore a vast open world filled with many building and areas</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Fight against the living and the dead</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Hunt animals for food </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Improve your skills overtime by gathering experience </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Trade goods with other survivors </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Build or occupy an existing house</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Collect or buy guns from other survivors</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Use tools to gather resources such as wood or minerals </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Burn down hordes of zombies</strong></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "One night the moon, which normally shone bright and white, had turned a deep, eerie shade of red. As the night wore on, people began to feel strange. They felt a hunger deep inside them, a hunger that could not be satisfied. It wasn't long before they began to turn on each other, attacking and biting those around them.<br>Before anyone knew it, people started to turn into zombies. They roamed the streets, seeking out any remaining survivors to feed on. Towns were overrun with the undead.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Explore a vast open world filled with many building and areas</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Fight against the living and the dead</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Hunt animals for food </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Improve your skills overtime by gathering experience </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Trade goods with other survivors </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Build or occupy an existing house</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Collect or buy guns from other survivors</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Use tools to gather resources such as wood or minerals </strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>- Burn down hordes of zombies</strong></h2>",
